channel.title: Need some professional assistance!
channel.description:
Hello,
I am planning on making or finding something that can decrypt PK servers hashed passwords. But i need help because I don't know the exact format it is getting saved in. I see it has things to do with Md5 but that is not the format, because i have a decryptor for that and thats not the format cuz md5 looks something like this: 4d5f28dfs66se8f4ss23w58 and the password coded in PK servers are more something like this: 589-648-523-486-452-178-698-24-5-69-87-1--336-987-123 Any help or assistance would be greatly appreciated.
Thanks,
eclipse245
